text: Tommy O'Hagan (born 5 October 1993) is an Irish rugby union player, currently playing for Pro14 and European Rugby Champions Cup side Ulster. He plays as a prop. ==Ulster== O'Hagan made his senior Ulster debut on 28 December 2018 in round 12 of the 2018–19 Pro14, featuring off the bench in the provinces 37–17 win against Scottish side Glasgow Warriors. ==References== ==External links== *Ulster Profile *Pro14 Profile * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Rugby union players from County Dublin Category:Irish rugby union players Category:Ulster Rugby players Category:Rugby union props
